cat("Hello aliens! I assure you we are not all wishing destruction upon the world. If, for some reason, you can read English, then please find some way to contact us, preferably through Carnegie Mellon University in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. Our outside-Earth research department is stellar and has some really nice people in the department, so please grant them the honor of our planet's first communications with beings fron out of this world! Regards, A Lowly Student")